{"tid":362678,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"周杰倫作的不只是歌，是藝術品","createTime":"2017-08-17T06:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T06:59:12.000Z","uid":58099,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c03b81226a8eaf2e6825d370fe42977bfe0f2135","tid":362678,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"首首歌都有非常華麗的編曲<br />\n<br />\n風鈴音，槍音，開門音，笛聲，摩打音<br />\n<br />\n玩得淋漓盡致<br />\n<br />\n每首歌曲調分明，<br />\n<br />\n節奏強烈，<br />\n<br />\n歌曲歌詞強烈畫面感<br />\n<br />\n有d 運用停頓技巧，<br />\n<br />\n有d用旋律分裂合唱法<br />\n<br />\n打鼓尾段突然雙擊技巧<br />\n<br />\n強勁優美的中國風音調<br />\n<br />\n副歌入肉到位的旋律<br />\n<br />\n簡直令人情緒盡舒<br />\n<br />\n自創rap 歌與旋律共存（頂級作品：因父之名，梯田）<br />\n<br />\n開創全新rap 的風格<br />\n<br />\n每首歌聽1000次<br />\n<br />\n都不能消化每個細節<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作曲，我只服周杰倫‼️"},{"pid":"50b285db8765b94c33c075054a90d106c6f23762","tid":362678,"uid":126305,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/142040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F142040_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5e4cc154&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55543f1bc89b63382812a90b62950f63ae27bde6","tid":362678,"uid":2313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"聽周杰倫都係聽佢非情歌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1784cfa1fb730dcaa88f596be60407c037daa937","tid":362678,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:51:04.000Z","msg":".,"},{"pid":"0a0220ea7f9d4cae181e247f78f36242e9dbfddf","tid":362678,"uid":17531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8088c375cebf2fd6c6f86cb194c39843aaadc9d","tid":362678,"uid":2313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11: